Patch notes link:<br><br><a href="https://forums.daybreakgames.com/ps2/index.php?threads/pc-game-update-8-15-fanning-the-fire-teams.250101/#post-3511809" class="postlink">CLICK HERE</a>.<br><br>Since this is a hell of a lot to copy, i will just get the most important stuff in here:<br><ul><li> Code Improvements</li><li> Warpgates stabilize after 3 hours -&gt; Faster triggering of alerts and better continent rotation</li><li> New Event: Gaining Ground. Capture Major Outposts and hold them to win</li><li> <strong class="text-strong"><span style="text-decoration:underline">Squad improvements:</span></strong></li><li> Mentor Squads can be opened now (Can't be turned into Platoons, especially for players below BR 15</li><li> New Visuals for Waypoints</li><li> Squads can be auto filled to Platoons (will see how that works exactly)</li><li> Squad map indicators show the direction Squad members are facing</li><li> Outfit hosted Platoons</li><li> Fireteam leaders have the ability to place beacons and waypoints</li><li> Orders chat has been removed</li><li> New building directive</li><li> Tons of new Implants and rebalance of existing Implants</li><li> Implants are now craftable with ISO-4</li><li> Vehicle rebalance</li><li> Some Infantry gun balance, and slight buff of Supressor and High Velocity Ammo</li><li> New Player studio stuff and Outfit decals, sadly no EDIM decal</li><li> Various other fixes</li></ul>That list is longer than expected, check out the patch notes for the rest.<br><br>Looks like a great patch!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://www.emeraldimmersion.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Pronix</a> — Thu Aug 16, 2018 10:41 am</p><hr />
